  "excerpt": "<p>My Etsy Picks: Gettin’ Lucky Fun Fact: While a week from today is Saint Patrick’s Day, a week from yesterday is my kitty’s birthday! Lucky turns the big 1-0 on Monday, March 16th! He was born mid-March and is a natural red-head, so he’s obviously Irish. But that is just part of why his name [&hellip;]</p>\n",
  "content": "<p><strong>My Etsy Picks: Gettin’ Lucky</strong></p>\n<p>Fun Fact: While a week from today is Saint Patrick’s Day, a week from yesterday is my kitty’s birthday! Lucky turns the big 1-0 on Monday, March 16th! He was born mid-March and is a natural red-head, so he’s obviously Irish. But that is just part of why his name is Lucky! He was actually named something else entirely (Sandy) when I adopted him, and I promptly renamed him something else (Murphy), but that just didn’t seem right. After a month of having him, I picked him up out of my dresser (he liked to sleep in the drawers) and he kept playing with the four-leaf clover necklace I had around my neck. He was obsessed! I called him my Lucky bear and it stuck. He was fated to have the name!</p>\n<p>Saint Patrick’s Day always makes me think of my little fuzzball, and obviously partly my heritage. I’m only a quarter Irish, but my husband is about 50% Irish, so our future children will definitely have it in them. We always celebrated with bright green outfits and soda bread, and today I’ll honor the upcoming holiday with some awesome handmade items from Etsy!</p>\n<p>You can see the <a title=\"Gettin' Lucky on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyNDc3MzQ0MQ/gettin-lucky\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>full treasury right here</strong></a>. Check out each of the shops below!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Noodles Nail Polish on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/179658936/erin-go-bragh-saint-patricks-day?ref=sr_gallery_11&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_ref=auto2&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Noodles Nail Polish</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"DayDogDesigns on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/223906740/green-shamrock-dog-collar-irish-saint?ref=sr_gallery_29&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_page=3&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>DayDogDesigns</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"DortDesigns on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/34688783/mini-beveled-shamrock-stained-glass?ref=sr_gallery_10&ga_search_query=shamrock&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_ref=auto2&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>DortDesigns</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Banner Cheer Jr. on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/153498946/lucky-st-patricks-day-irish-sign?ref=sr_gallery_10&ga_search_query=lucky&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Banner Cheer Jr.</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Lime Green Modern on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/159543623/silver-four-leaf-clover-necklace?ref=sr_gallery_2&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_page=4&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Lime Green Modern</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Crimson Hill Soapworks on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/179962281/shamrock-soap-st-patricks-day-irish-gold?ref=sr_gallery_33&ga_search_query=4+leaf+clover&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_ref=auto2&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Crimson Hill Soapworks</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Trendy Stop on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/225119615/white-shamrocks-print-infinity-scarf?ref=sr_gallery_34&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_page=6&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Trendy Stop</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Munchkin and Bean on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/203664517/saint-patricks-day-felt-board?ref=sr_gallery_31&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_ref=auto2&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Munchkin and Bean</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Mister Scribbles on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/223299512/lucky-in-love-notebook-journal-st?ref=sr_gallery_7&ga_search_query=lucky&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Mister Scribbles</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Po's Bag of Bones Bakery on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/68302825/leprechauns-gold-dog-treats-saint?ref=sr_gallery_14&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_ref=auto2&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Po’s Bag of Bones Bakery</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"The Pendant Island on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/124227134/clover-necklace-clover-pendant-clover?ref=sr_gallery_11&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_page=2&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>The Pendant Island</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Cuddle Sleep Dream on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/179028715/st-patricks-day-cardigan-with-bowtie?ref=sr_gallery_40&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_ref=auto2&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Cuddle Sleep Dream</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Primitive Wood Signs on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/222980678/24-shamrock-sign-4-leaf-clover-wood?ref=sr_gallery_27&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_ref=auto2&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Primitive Wood Signs</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Hen House Originals on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/177441690/i-love-ireland-pillow-cover-irish-green?ref=sr_gallery_15&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_ref=auto2&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Hen House Originals</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"WVLuckygirl's Primitive Store on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/175487848/unstuffed-primitive-pillow-saint?ref=sr_gallery_37&ga_search_query=saint+patricks+day&ga_order=most_relevant&ga_explicit_scope=1&ga_page=2&ga_search_type=handmade&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>WVLuckygirl’s Primitive Store</strong></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Rain Dancer Clothing on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/224068661/st-patricks-day-womens-tri-blend-workout?ref=sr_gallery_11&ga_search_query=womens+st+patricks+day+shirt&ga_page=7&ga_search_type=all&ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Rain Dancer Clothing</strong></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Which item is your favorite?</p>\n",
